name: tired pixels #14
description:
somewhere here will appear my prose
and if you do not look for enemies among people
the rose of peace will bloom on earth
we will be freed from invisible shackles
 the magician was not crucified like Jesus
he was pecked by a dove of peace
miracle turned out to taste
at the play he was not a fakir
 but don't be afraid everything will be as before
there will be time to stand and move eternity
people will love without clothes
buying carelessness with money
